+1 for the PR, but I believe it should be configured like this:

```
assetic:
    filters:
        compass:
            sass_options:
                cache_location:  "%some_dir%"
```

to make it reflect the structure of compass config more precisely (https://github.com/kriswallsmith/assetic/blob/master/src/Assetic/Filter/CompassFilter.php#L191)

